<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    Hi <%= @volunteer.name.split.first.capitalize %>,
    <p>
    Thank you for volunteering tomorrow, <%= @logs.first.when.strftime("%b %e") %>!<br>
    Below are the details for your shift<%= @logs.length > 1 ? "s" : "" %>:
    </p>

    <ul>
    <% @logs.each{ |l| %>
      <li>
        <strong>Collection location: <%= l.donor.nil? ? "Unknown" : l.donor.name %></strong> (<%= readable_start_time(l.schedule_chain) %>)<br>
        Volunteers: <%= l.volunteers.collect{ |v| v.nil? ? nil : v.name.split.first.capitalize }.compact.join(", ") %><br>
        Lead Volunteer: <%= l.lead_volunteer.name.split.first.capitalize %> - <%= l.lead_volunteer.phone %><br><br>
        
        <strong>Delivery locations:</strong><br>
        <%= l.recipients.collect{ |r| r.nil? ? nil : r.name }.compact.join("<br>").html_safe %><br><br>
      </li>
    <% } %>
    </ul>

    <p>
      <strong>The next Arlington Food Pantry distribution date is:</strong><br>
      <%= @pantry.strftime("%A, %b %e %Y") %>
    </p>

    If you have any questions or canâ€™t make your shift, please reply to this email as soon as possible.

    <p>Thanks!</p>
    <p>The Food Link Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
